<subSubSection pageId="290" pageNumber="291" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="290" pageNumber="291">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="290" pageNumber="291">This species has been reported from southeastern Louisiana (Colby 2002: 37), southern Florida (Darlington 1935a: 161), the Bahamas (Peck and Thomas 1998: 18), Cuba (Darlington 1934: 70), Cayman Islands and Puerto Rico (Peck 2005: 29), Dominican Republic (Erwin 2011b: 204), Jamaica, and eastern Mexico in Veracruz and Campeche (Nichols 1988a: 181).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
